          </ul></div><div id="posts"><article class="post type-text" id="798066644"><aside class="metadata not-custom-page"><a class="timestamp" href="lesson-9-consonants-part-1-and">July 12th, 2010</a><!--  
                               <a class="note-count" href="http://www.learning-hindi.com/post/798066644/lesson-9-consonants-part-1-क-ka-ख-kha-ग-ga-घ#notes">17 notes</a> --><a class="comment-count" href="lesson-9-consonants-part-1-and#disqus_thread"></a><script type="text/javascript">
